  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276900/extras/b74d08906817598e4c0c529fd78b0f5a.avif?t=1743178510\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276900/extras_big/b74d08906817598e4c0c529fd78b0f5a.avif?t=1743178510 width=800 height=224 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Narrative driven puzzle/precision platformer.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Over 100 levels to challenge your mind and reflexes.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tons of secrets, hidden pickups and easter eggs.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hundreds of Outfits, Hats and Pets to customize your look.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A plethora of friendly (and not so friendly) NPCs.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A multitude of special abilities and powers.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenge rooms to test your skill and sanity.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pixel art brought to life at 60fps.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dozens of enemy variations.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Several mini games including fishing and slot machines.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Over 40 unlockable achievements.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game stat tracking across 3 save slots.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Xbox and Playstation Gamepad support.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customizable controls.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Retro soundtrack spanning 20 songs</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlockable Speedrun and Hardcore modes.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In game photo taking and viewing.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
